column5: We'll fella's i'm back from Kesagami. I didn't want to leave, and I had a great summer. I saw lots of fish despite consistantly bad weather. Hope the summer is going well for all of you.  Tight Lines  -R-
Must suck leaving paradise this year.  Especially seeings as there's more water and the bugs are finally settling down.  I leave next wednesday Dave.  You have to have that report up by Tuesday. lol.
Welcome back.  Saw you in a past issue of Ontario Out of Doors releasing a big pike at Kasagami, Congrats.
Welcome Back!  It was great seeing you again at Kesagami this summer!!  Greg
Welcome back R.O. Glad it all went well. Looking forward to reading the journal. :-)
